First, we assume you have a lib crate named as `rust_from_c`.
`lib.rs` should have Rust code as following:

#[unsafe(no_mangle)]
pub extern "C" fn hello_from_rust() {
    println!("Hello from Rust!");
}

paragraphs.nomicon_rust_side_p2:
#[unsafe(no_mangle)]
pub extern "C" fn hello_from_rust() {
